"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Apr 22, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104lmt1718875974603.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lmt1718875974603.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lmt1718875974603.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"tgs1665703008360\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $lowercase\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"tgs1665703008360___lowercase_274444\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Convert a string to lowercase.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"tgs1665703008360__topic_d85907e1_d85908e1_d85909e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tgs1665703008360__p_d85910e1_d85911e1_d85912e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$lowercase</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">String</var> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">\"NlsLocale\"</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">\"classic\"</code> } <code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"tgs1665703008360__section_w2475ab1b7b5_w2476ab1b7_w2477ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tgs1665703008360__p_d85913e1_d85914e1_d85915e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">vConverted = $lowercase (\"The STRING\", \"nlslocale\")</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tgs1665703008360__topic_d57102e1_d57103e1_d57104e1_d57105e1_d57106e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d730902e94\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"tgs1665703008360__table_d9074e1_d9075e1_d9076e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"tgs1665703008360__table_d9074e1_d9075e1_d9076e1__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"tgs1665703008360__table_d9074e1_d9075e1_d9076e1__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"tgs1665703008360__table_d9074e1_d9075e1_d9076e1__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgs1665703008360__table_d9074e1_d9075e1_d9076e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">String</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgs1665703008360__table_d9074e1_d9075e1_d9076e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgs1665703008360__table_d9074e1_d9075e1_d9076e1__entry__3\">\n String to convert to lowercase; can be a string, field (or indirect reference to a field), variable, or function that evaluates to a string.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgs1665703008360__table_d9074e1_d9075e1_d9076e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">NlsLocale</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgs1665703008360__table_d9074e1_d9075e1_d9076e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgs1665703008360__table_d9074e1_d9075e1_d9076e1__entry__3\">Apply locale-based rules based on the value of\n                        the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$nlslocale</span>, as specified by\n                           <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$nlslocale</span> or <code class=\"ph codeph\">$NLS_LOCALE</code>. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgs1665703008360__table_d9074e1_d9075e1_d9076e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">classic</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgs1665703008360__table_d9074e1_d9075e1_d9076e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"tgs1665703008360__table_d9074e1_d9075e1_d9076e1__entry__3\">\n Ignore locale when converting data; apply one-to-one character conversion according to Unicode definitions.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tgs1665703008360__topic_d57107e1_d57108e1_d57109e1_d57110e1_d57111e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d730902e193\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tgs1665703008360__p_d85922e1_d85923e1_d85924e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">String</var> converted to lowercase.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tgs1665703008360__topic_d57112e1_d57113e1_d57114e1_d57115e1_d57116e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d730902e206\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tgs1665703008360__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tgs1665703008360__topic_d57117e1_d57118e1_d57119e1_d57120e1_d57121e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d730902e215\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tgs1665703008360__p_d85934e1_d85935e1_d85936e1\">The way in which strings are converted depends on the NLS settings in effect. If the second argument is omitted, the value of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$nlscase</span> is used to determine case conversion behavior. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xfm1665702676151.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xfm1665702676151.html\" title=\"You can use ProcScript statements and functions to convert string from uppercase to lowercase or from lowercase to uppercase. The default conversion behavior is determined by the values of NLS assignment settings and ProcScript functions, which control locale-based processing.\">Case Conversion</a>.</p>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">For example, the following ProcScript converts the Turkish word <code class=\"ph codeph\">KIPIRTI</code> to lowercase as <code class=\"ph codeph\">kipirti</code>.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">FIELD1 = $lowercase (\"KIPIRTI\", \"classic\")\n;Result: FIELD1 = kipirti</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">However, Turkish has both a dotted <code class=\"ph codeph\">i</code> and an undotted <code class=\"ph codeph\">ı</code>, so this case conversion is incorrect. To get the correct conversion, you need to set the locale to Turkish, so that locale-based case conversion is applied.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$nlslocale = \"tr_TR\" ; set locale to Turkish(Turkey)\nFIELD2 = $lowercase (\"KIPIRTI\")\nResult: FIELD2 = kıpırtı</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xfm1665702676151.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Case Conversion</a><p>You can use ProcScript statements and functions to convert string from uppercase to lowercase or from lowercase to uppercase. The default conversion behavior is determined by the values of NLS assignment settings and ProcScript functions, which control locale-based processing.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rnc1665703005296.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>lowercase (deprecated)</a><p>Convert a string to lowercase.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xuh1718876337843.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$uppercase</a><p>Convert the specified string uppercase.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zbh1665703006270.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uppercase (deprecated)</a><p>Convert the specified string to uppercase.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7422028\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7422028\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$lowercase Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Apr 22, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $lowercase Convert a string to lowercase. $lowercase ( String { , \"NlsLocale\" | \"classic\" } ) Example: vConverted = $lowercase (\"The STRING\", \"nlslocale\") Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description String String String to convert to lowercase; can be a string, field (or indirect reference to a field), variable, or function that evaluates to a string. NlsLocale String Apply locale-based rules based on the value of the $nlslocale , as specified by $nlslocale or $NLS_LOCALE . classic String Ignore locale when converting data; apply one-to-one character conversion according to Unicode definitions. Return Values String converted to lowercase. Use Allowed in all component types. Description The way in which strings are converted depends on the NLS settings in effect. If the second argument is omitted, the value of $nlscase is used to determine case conversion behavior. For more information, see Case Conversion . For example, the following ProcScript converts the Turkish word KIPIRTI to lowercase as kipirti . FIELD1 = $lowercase (\"KIPIRTI\", \"classic\") ;Result: FIELD1 = kipirti Copy However, Turkish has both a dotted i and an undotted ı , so this case conversion is incorrect. To get the correct conversion, you need to set the locale to Turkish, so that locale-based case conversion is applied. $nlslocale = \"tr_TR\" ; set locale to Turkish(Turkey) FIELD2 = $lowercase (\"KIPIRTI\") Result: FIELD2 = kıpırtı Copy Related Links Case Conversion You can use ProcScript statements and functions to convert string from uppercase to lowercase or from lowercase to uppercase. The default conversion behavior is determined by the values of NLS assignment settings and ProcScript functions, which control locale-based processing. lowercase (deprecated) Convert a string to lowercase. $uppercase Convert the specified string uppercase. uppercase (deprecated) Convert the specified string to uppercase. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}